83
00:05:23,990 --> 00:05:25,320
but have to rely on them.

84
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:27,170
Sometimes,

85
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,440
only by lying

86
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:31,410
can the truth be revealed.

87
00:05:33,250 --> 00:05:34,150
To me,

88
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:36,520
lies are more like a means,

89
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:37,330
a means

90
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:40,120
to make others pay.

91
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,280
Well, look at you.

92
00:05:52,960 --> 00:05:54,720
You're a scumbag tester.

93
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:55,960
Aren't you doing this

94
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:57,580
