99
00:06:05,550 --> 00:06:08,800
"Love can't be tested by lies."

100
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:12,280
You were stalking that dog owner every day.

101
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,200
What dog owner?

102
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:16,590
I was helping the girl find her dog.

103
00:06:16,860 --> 00:06:17,260
Okay.

104
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:17,950
Got it.

105
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:24,220
Why didn't you ask me

106
00:06:24,250 --> 00:06:26,110
