107
00:06:28,790 --> 00:06:31,320
Then why did you choose to be a scumbag tester?

108
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,290
When I was in college,

109
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:36,520
one of my roommates

110
00:06:37,070 --> 00:06:38,880
was fooled by her first love.

111
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:41,070
That man was getting married,

112
00:06:41,070 --> 00:06:42,520
but he still kept it from her.

113
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:44,770
Not only did he cheat her out of her scholarship,

114
00:06:44,770 --> 00:06:47,150
but he also asked her to borrow money from the online loan platform for him.

115
00:06:47,150 --> 00:06:49,360
We had no choice

116
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,680
but to set up a trap

117
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,600
to reveal his true nature.

118
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,040
So,

119
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:58,030
you decided to become a scumbag tester later?

120
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:03,720
Actually, people are good at lying to themselves.

121
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:06,120
Especially when something goes wrong

122
00:07:06,150 --> 00:07:08,180
with their heartfelt relationship.

123
00:07:08,180 --> 00:07:09,050
Instinctively,

124
00:07:09,050 --> 00:07:11,520
they choose to escape from our true feelings.

125
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:12,720
So at this time,

126
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:15,510
they need to break the lie.

127
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:20,000
I know my job is shady.

128
00:07:20,710 --> 00:07:21,950
But I think

129
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:25,460
that there is always someone who needs someone like me.

130
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:29,360
If I ever lose my job,

131
00:07:29,490 --> 00:07:30,920
I'll become a scumbag tester with you.

132
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:31,980
We'll be

133
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:33,720
