224
00:11:54,390 --> 00:11:55,600
Nothing will do.

225
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:04,540
-No need to call any of them.
-Let’s get back to work.

226
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:13,560
Miss Su,

227
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:14,760
