228
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:15,370
No.

229
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:16,000
Thank you.

230
00:12:20,100 --> 00:12:21,260
Here's the thing.

231
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:23,400
Mr. Zhou has reviewed your resume

232
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:25,000
