233
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,950
for the position of resort architect at our company.

234
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:28,880
That's why I invited you here.

235
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:30,550
I thought

236
00:12:30,550 --> 00:12:32,810
that Mr. Zhou would eliminate my resume.

237
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,000
No way.

238
00:12:35,390 --> 00:12:35,960
Miss Su,

239
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:38,420
