261
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:42,880
About Jiang Lai...

262
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:43,480
Mr. Zhou.

263
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,660
We're here to talk about work.

264
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:47,880
Okay.

265
00:13:49,860 --> 00:13:51,910
Architecture major at Cambridge University.

266
00:13:51,910 --> 00:13:53,680
Internal awards: the International Hospitality Design Landscape of the Year Award

267
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:56,280
