275
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:17,110
Here's the thing.

276
00:14:17,110 --> 00:14:18,150
I believe I'm the perfect candidate

277
00:14:18,150 --> 00:14:20,080
for the Dream City Resort project.

278
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:23,060
