00:15:18,940 --> 00:15:19,720
I don't think so.

293
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:20,520
She is...

294
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,080
Why not?

295
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:21,600
Stop it.

296
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,720
No chitchat at work!

297
00:15:28,610 --> 00:15:29,400
Yes.

298
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:35,730
Let's get down to business.

299
00:15:41,290 --> 00:15:41,840
Mr. Zhou.

300
00:15:42,880 --> 00:15:43,680
Contract?

301
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:52,640
What contract?

302
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:54,360
They're going to sign the labor contract now?

303
00:15:54,360 --> 00:15:54,890
No way.

304
00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:55,910
That fast!

305
00:15:57,990 --> 00:15:59,570
The speed of lightning.

306
00:16:18,760 --> 00:16:21,220
Actually, your father came to me yesterday.

307
00:16:22,390 --> 00:16:24,250
He gave me a letter of appointment

308
00:16:25,070 --> 00:16:27,800
and designated me as the architect of the resort.

309
00:16:30,400 --> 00:16:31,660
I guess

310
00:16:32,190 --> 00:16:33,190
you didn't agree.

311
00:16:33,560 --> 00:16:34,550
How did you know?

312
00:16:36,560 --> 00:16:37,860
With your resume,

313
00:16:37,880 --> 00:16:40,000
why give the initiative to others?

314
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:42,750
I made the right choice.

315
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:45,600
When can we start working?

316
00:16:47,920 --> 00:16:48,600
Anytime.

317
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:51,560
Let's do it now.

318
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:53,600
Introduce your employees to me.

319
00:16:54,560 --> 00:16:55,040
Okay.

320
00:16:55,920 --> 00:16:57,850
This is called scraping, you know?

321
00:16:57,880 --> 00:16:58,640
It can relax your meridians.

322
00:16:58,640 --> 00:16:59,350
Mr. Zhou.

323
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:00,240
Mr. Zhou.

324
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:01,870
Let me introduce.

325
00:17:01,870 --> 00:17:02,730
This is Ma Shan.

326
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:03,160
It's me.

327
00:17:03,160 --> 00:17:04,130
This is Ye Tingting.

328
00:17:04,130 --> 00:17:05,060
-Hello.
-Hello.

329
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,160
And this one.

330
00:17:10,099 --> 00:17:11,099
This is Jiang Lai,

331
00:17:11,359 --> 00:17:13,020
also part of the secretariat.

332
00:17:18,520 --> 00:17:18,960
Hello.

333
00:17:19,060 --> 00:17:20,020
Let me formally introduce myself.

334
00:17:20,020 --> 00:17:20,859
I'm Su Qing.

335
00:17:23,560 --> 00:17:23,990
Hello.

336
00:17:24,020 --> 00:17:25,150
My name is Jiang Lai.

337
00:17:27,829 --> 00:17:30,500
[Hotel]

338
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:02,160
How is it?

339
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:04,720
Haven’t you figured out what to say?

340
00:18:10,320 --> 00:18:12,040
What business dealings do you have

341
00:18:12,040 --> 00:18:13,640
with Zhou Mingde and Sun Wei?

342
00:18:21,420 --> 00:18:22,300
Your men

343
00:18:22,320 --> 00:18:24,380
have been arrested for over 24 hours.

344
00:18:24,560 --> 00:18:27,490
The police are also looking for you all over the city.

345
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:36,760
Call me when you come around.

346
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:38,290
If it takes too long,

347
00:18:38,470 --> 00:18:40,470
I may not be able to cover you either.

348
00:19:15,580 --> 00:19:16,420
Everyone,

349
00:19:16,440 --> 00:19:17,360
any questions?

350
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:20,810
Okay.

351
00:19:21,600 --> 00:19:22,660
It's settled then.

352
00:19:24,280 --> 00:19:24,840
Dismiss.

353
00:19:29,860 --> 00:19:30,990
Wait for me a moment.

354
00:19:31,780 --> 00:19:32,410
Chen Jun.

355
00:19:36,260 --> 00:19:37,660
What do we have for lunch?

356
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:40,530
The pickled vegetables and fish downstairs?

357
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:43,670
A construction truck was crushed in Wanlongxi yesterday.

358
00:19:43,670 --> 00:19:45,600
The shop's fish are all from there.

359
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:47,890
Then what should we eat?

360
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:51,570
Order takeout from Grandma's Home?

361
00:19:51,590 --> 00:19:52,310
How is it?

362
00:19:52,360 --> 00:19:53,060
Not bad.

363
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:55,520
Don’t order the one in Hengyu Square.

364
00:19:55,600 --> 00:19:57,070
They have a fire inspection today.

365
00:19:57,070 --> 00:19:58,130
It'll be very slow.

366
00:19:58,310 --> 00:20:00,200
Then order from the restaurant on Hongshan Road.

367
00:20:00,200 --> 00:20:00,840
That should be fine.

368
00:20:00,840 --> 00:20:01,580
Let me see.

369
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:02,560
Jun.

370
00:20:03,350 --> 00:20:05,230
Do you want to order takeout together?

371
00:20:05,230 --> 00:20:06,150
No.

372
00:20:06,310 --> 00:20:09,040
I have a date with my girlfriend at Lushan Braise.

373
00:20:09,380 --> 00:20:11,400
Are you going to that restaurant again?

374
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:12,160
At this hour,

375
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:13,560
the Lingshan Tunnel should be jammed.

376
00:20:13,560 --> 00:20:14,280
Take a detour.

377
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:15,300
Take Beishan Street.

378
00:20:15,300 --> 00:20:16,830
Is it the one on Huanxi Road?

379
00:20:16,920 --> 00:20:17,480
Yes.

380
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:20,310
Mr. Zhou, are you free

381
00:20:20,310 --> 00:20:21,800
to have lunch with me?

382
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:27,200
I'm sorry.

383
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:29,160
I have a date with my girlfriend.

384
00:20:31,520 --> 00:20:32,850
I have something to say.

385
00:20:33,950 --> 00:20:34,540
How about

386
00:20:34,570 --> 00:20:35,760
after the lunch break, okay?

387
00:20:35,760 --> 00:20:37,070
It concerns everyone.

388
00:20:37,390 --> 00:20:39,190
I think it's better to talk here.

389
00:20:41,120 --> 00:20:41,640
Okay.

390
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:42,360
Go ahead.

391
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:43,880
Here's the thing.

392
00:20:44,190 --> 00:20:45,590
My friends in the studio

393
00:20:45,620 --> 00:20:46,260
will help me finish the design drawings

394
00:20:46,260 --> 00:20:48,360
for the resort in England.

395
00:20:48,360 --> 00:20:50,810
But I need to do the field surveys

396
00:20:50,830 --> 00:20:52,270
in China.

397
00:20:52,520 --> 00:20:53,360
So,

398
00:20:53,500 --> 00:20:56,050
I need to apply for a colleague within the company

399
00:20:56,050 --> 00:20:56,980
as my assistant,

400
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:58,320
someone who is familiar

401
00:20:58,320 --> 00:20:59,600
with this project.

402
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:03,250
It seems you have found a suitable candidate.

403
00:21:04,850 --> 00:21:05,840
I want Jiang Lai.

404
00:21:09,740 --> 00:21:10,640
Jiang Lai?

405
00:21:10,700 --> 00:21:11,400
Jiang Lai, I...

406
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:12,120
I can do it.

407
00:21:15,660 --> 00:21:16,660
That's it.

408
00:21:16,690 --> 00:21:17,720
Time is running out.

409
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:18,390
Mr. Zhou,

410
00:21:18,420 --> 00:21:20,750
let me borrow your girlfriend for a while.

411
00:21:27,360 --> 00:21:29,080
Didn't we have a lunch date?

412
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:31,160
Mr. Zhou.

413
00:21:32,350 --> 00:21:33,040
What?

414
00:21:33,440 --> 00:21:34,240
Move over, please.

415
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:35,170
I'm in a hurry.

416
00:21:35,200 --> 00:21:36,660
[Well, I'll go first. Hurry up]

417
00:21:37,080 --> 00:21:37,390
Let's go.

418
00:21:37,390 --> 00:21:38,120
Go.

419
00:21:41,200 --> 00:21:41,860
Mr. Zhou.

420
00:21:41,980 --> 00:21:42,500
I'm busy catching the subway.

421
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:43,170
It's rush hour.

422
00:21:43,170 --> 00:21:44,570
We're all busy.

423
00:21:44,850 --> 00:21:47,660
[Meeting Room]

424
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:57,150
Are you nervous?

425
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:01,160
Yes.

426
00:22:01,940 --> 00:22:03,440
You suddenly chose me, the least experienced,

427
00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:04,680
to be your assistant.

428
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:09,040
Plus, we had unusual interactions before.

429
00:22:10,370 --> 00:22:11,910
So I'm a little nervous.

430
00:22:12,910 --> 00:22:14,560
You are quite interesting.

431
00:22:15,430 --> 00:22:17,690
Then why did you agree to be my assistant?

432
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:23,170
Because I need this chance more than anyone else.

433
00:22:23,200 --> 00:22:24,870
And I've read your resume before.

434
00:22:24,870 --> 00:22:26,720
You're excellent and professional.

435
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:30,040
I always believe in leaving professional matters to the professionals.

436
00:22:30,040 --> 00:22:31,000
So, at least,

437
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:32,280
you chose me

438
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:34,730
because it's related to your work needs.

439
00:22:35,100 --> 00:22:36,830
I chose you for only one reason.

440
00:22:37,120 --> 00:22:38,850
I am impressed by your ability.

441
00:22:39,940 --> 00:22:41,560
When we were in the meeting room,

442
00:22:41,560 --> 00:22:44,120
you could tell the exact food source,

443
00:22:44,120 --> 00:22:45,360
urban road planning,

444
00:22:45,840 --> 00:22:47,900
and even the current news of the mall.

445
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:50,440
I think you must know this city well.

446
00:22:51,920 --> 00:22:52,820
Indeed.

447
00:22:53,520 --> 00:22:54,880
I grew up here.

448
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:57,410
Plus, my previous job

449
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:59,760
makes me know this place better than others.

450
00:22:59,760 --> 00:23:01,440
If I want to design the construction plan,

451
00:23:01,440 --> 00:23:03,520
I need to know the city's orientation,

452
00:23:03,520 --> 00:23:05,240
the surrounding environment,

453
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:06,650
and even local customs and practices.

454
00:23:06,650 --> 00:23:08,690
So, you need me to be your tour guide?

455
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:10,240
Yes.

456
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:13,360
Now you need this job,

457
00:23:13,800 --> 00:23:15,310
and I need your ability.

458
00:23:15,680 --> 00:23:18,680
We're kind of like a community with shared interests.

459
00:23:18,960 --> 00:23:20,440
So, next...

460
00:23:21,200 --> 00:23:23,400
I'd appreciate it if you'd tell me more.

461
00:23:28,380 --> 00:23:30,820
