00:23:30,840 --> 00:23:33,750
♫Snapdragon flowers dancing against the breeze♫

463
00:23:35,540 --> 00:23:37,960
♫The sunshine lights up ahead♫

464
00:23:38,120 --> 00:23:41,030
♫Plant the seeds of our love in the soil♫

465
00:23:42,760 --> 00:23:45,230
♫Let's go on our splendid journey now♫

466
00:23:45,250 --> 00:23:48,640
♫Let's enjoy the blooming season together♫

467
00:23:50,060 --> 00:23:53,060
♫Open our hearts and let each other in♫

468
00:23:53,090 --> 00:23:55,470
♫Don't lie to me again♫

469
00:23:57,220 --> 00:24:00,460
♫Facing the wind, leave behind all the doubts♫

470
00:24:00,960 --> 00:24:04,180
♫Let's look out for our harbour together♫

471
00:24:04,670 --> 00:24:07,530
♫When you're with me, I can never feel lost♫

