00:24:07,140 --> 00:24:10,840
[Where are you]

473
00:24:07,550 --> 00:24:09,390
♫My eyes are locked on yours♫

474
00:24:09,410 --> 00:24:10,920
♫The way you look♫

475
00:24:10,870 --> 00:24:12,870
[Field trip near the resort]

476
00:24:11,390 --> 00:24:12,540
♫The starlight♫

477
00:24:12,560 --> 00:24:14,480
♫And the sweetness from the field♫

478
00:24:14,500 --> 00:24:15,720
♫I'm not going to step back♫

479
00:24:14,790 --> 00:24:15,520
Jiang Lai.

480
00:24:15,610 --> 00:24:16,890
We can see the whole view of the resort

481
00:24:15,740 --> 00:24:16,740
♫I'm walking to you♫

482
00:24:16,760 --> 00:24:18,570
♫I want to stop the time♫

483
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:19,080
from that mountain, right?

484
00:24:18,600 --> 00:24:20,490
♫It's raining♫

485
00:24:20,520 --> 00:24:21,580
♫The flowers are blooming♫

486
00:24:21,330 --> 00:24:22,320
I think so.

487
00:24:22,510 --> 00:24:23,340
♫Look up♫

488
00:24:23,360 --> 00:24:24,960
♫Let's look at the starry night♫

489
00:24:23,440 --> 00:24:24,990
Let's go up the hill and have a look.

490
00:24:24,990 --> 00:24:27,740
♫With the truth only, I'm walking to you♫

491
00:24:27,720 --> 00:24:28,720
It's hard to climb that mountain.

492
00:24:27,760 --> 00:24:29,430
♫I'll tell you about my past♫

493
00:24:28,720 --> 00:24:30,480
And you're wearing high heels.

494
00:24:29,450 --> 00:24:30,810
♫The beautiful woods♫

495
00:24:30,840 --> 00:24:32,190
♫Will witness my vow♫

496
00:24:31,020 --> 00:24:32,590
What if it gets dark when we climb up?

497
00:24:32,220 --> 00:24:33,430
♫I'm standing on the land of my hometown♫

498
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:33,770
It's okay.

499
00:24:33,790 --> 00:24:35,000
Let's just go up

500
00:24:35,030 --> 00:24:36,320
and come down quickly.

501
00:24:36,350 --> 00:24:37,350
I still have you.

502
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:37,710
Let's go.

503
00:24:37,710 --> 00:24:38,710
Go back to the car.

504
00:24:48,280 --> 00:24:49,540
I'll pick you up later.

505
00:24:56,080 --> 00:24:56,800
Hello.

506
00:24:58,160 --> 00:24:58,440
Yes.

507
00:24:58,440 --> 00:24:59,350
I'm Zhou Yu.

508
00:25:00,590 --> 00:25:01,320
Song Biao.

509
00:25:02,280 --> 00:25:03,680
I don't know this person.

510
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:06,840
I know.

511
00:25:06,870 --> 00:25:08,530
I will do my best to cooperate.

512
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:14,520
Mr. Zhou,

513
00:25:14,820 --> 00:25:16,010
I've found the email address

514
00:25:16,010 --> 00:25:17,210
you asked me to check.

515
00:25:18,210 --> 00:25:19,270
Who sent the email?

516
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:20,920
That email address is

517
00:25:20,950 --> 00:25:23,480
the printing store owner's private account.

518
00:25:23,490 --> 00:25:24,310
After we contacted him,

519
00:25:24,310 --> 00:25:25,350
he said

520
00:25:25,920 --> 00:25:27,200
that when the email was sent,

521
00:25:27,200 --> 00:25:28,680
he went to the toilet.

522
00:25:28,980 --> 00:25:31,700
It so happened that the surveillance cameras in his shop are broken these days.

523
00:25:31,700 --> 00:25:32,710
So, we don't know

524
00:25:32,730 --> 00:25:33,930
who sent the email.

525
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:34,870
Yes.

526
00:25:35,070 --> 00:25:37,670
The person who sent the email is very cautious.

527
00:25:48,070 --> 00:25:49,850
[Song Biao]

528
00:25:48,620 --> 00:25:49,180
Boss.

529
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:49,720
Well...

530
00:25:49,750 --> 00:25:51,590
Who is Song Biao?

531
00:25:52,510 --> 00:25:54,600
The police just called me,

532
00:25:54,720 --> 00:25:57,920
saying that a man named Song Biao planned the kidnapping.

533
00:25:58,090 --> 00:25:59,700
But his men only know

534
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:01,720
that he kidnapped Su Qing for money,

535
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:02,590
and they don't know

536
00:26:02,590 --> 00:26:03,550
who he turned to.

537
00:26:04,450 --> 00:26:06,300
Song Biao didn't contact you.

538
00:26:06,330 --> 00:26:08,180
Then he must have contacted the person who sent the email.

539
00:26:08,180 --> 00:26:09,660
As long as we can find Song Biao...

540
00:26:09,660 --> 00:26:10,580
We can find out

541
00:26:10,840 --> 00:26:12,000
who sent the email

542
00:26:12,600 --> 00:26:14,200
and why he kidnapped Su Qing?

543
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:41,070
Are you okay?

544
00:26:52,720 --> 00:26:53,640
Can we reach the peak

545
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:55,000
this way?

546
00:26:57,280 --> 00:26:58,160
I'll go up first.

547
00:26:58,160 --> 00:26:59,220
You do what you can.

548
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:24,720
Right.

549
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:28,240
Get back to me, and I'll see your suggestion.

550
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:28,880
Okay.

551
00:27:29,670 --> 00:27:30,210
Bye bye.

552
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:35,640
Look.

553
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:36,700
What's that place?

554
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:38,760
There?

555
00:27:39,690 --> 00:27:40,560
That's my peach garden.

556
00:27:40,560 --> 00:27:41,960
The one you just visited.

557
00:27:42,360 --> 00:27:43,420
What is over there?

558
00:27:45,410 --> 00:27:47,120
That's a patch of sycamore trees.

559
00:27:47,120 --> 00:27:49,720
Zhou Yu plans to build a treehouse hotel there.

560
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:51,330
Look over there.

561
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:52,940
Over that white house.

562
00:27:53,070 --> 00:27:55,000
That's my aunt's Snapdragon Farm.

563
00:27:59,200 --> 00:27:59,960
Are you and Zhou Yu together

564
00:27:59,960 --> 00:28:01,680
because of the resort?

565
00:28:04,870 --> 00:28:06,150
Not exactly.

566
00:28:07,520 --> 00:28:08,670
At first, we got to know each other

567
00:28:08,670 --> 00:28:10,500
because of the resort project.

568
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:12,910
But later,

569
00:28:13,280 --> 00:28:15,610
we went through something else together.

570
00:28:18,350 --> 00:28:19,230
It seems

571
00:28:19,560 --> 00:28:20,960
that I came back too late.

572
00:28:24,410 --> 00:28:25,450
I like Zhou Yu.

573
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:28,700
I want to compete with you fairly for him.

574
00:28:29,390 --> 00:28:30,180
I know

575
00:28:30,600 --> 00:28:32,440
that Zhou Yu only has eyes for you.

576
00:28:32,440 --> 00:28:33,600
But I won't give up.

577
00:28:33,920 --> 00:28:35,840
At least I won't have any regrets

578
00:28:36,370 --> 00:28:38,500
after fighting hard for the man I love.

579
00:28:39,330 --> 00:28:41,060
I believe in our relationship.

580
00:28:41,350 --> 00:28:42,950
And I also believe in myself.

581
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:58,350
The sun is setting.

582
00:28:58,640 --> 00:28:59,440
Let’s go back.

583
00:29:26,200 --> 00:29:26,910
Jiang Lai.

584
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:29,540
Why are you going downhill so slowly?

585
00:29:30,120 --> 00:29:31,000
Wait for me.

586
00:29:35,800 --> 00:29:36,880
Su Qing!

587
00:29:42,320 --> 00:29:43,090
Jiang Lai!

588
00:29:43,430 --> 00:29:44,050
Su Qing!

589
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:45,640
Su Qing!

590
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:48,560
Su Qing!

591
00:29:49,310 --> 00:29:49,990
I'm here.

592
00:29:50,280 --> 00:29:51,160
Are you okay?

593
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:52,360
I'm fine.

594
00:29:54,710 --> 00:29:55,510
What's wrong?

595
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:58,440
I think I sprained my ankle.

596
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:00,480
I should have listened to you

597
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:02,250
and walked slowly.

598
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:03,600
It's okay.

599
00:30:03,600 --> 00:30:04,520
I'll come down and help you.

600
00:30:04,520 --> 00:30:05,100
Okay.

601
00:30:05,260 --> 00:30:06,030
Be careful.

602
00:30:11,760 --> 00:30:12,560
No.

603
00:30:12,560 --> 00:30:13,690
It's too dangerous.

604
00:30:17,160 --> 00:30:18,520
My phone is missing.

605
00:30:18,560 --> 00:30:20,080
You call for help.

606
00:30:25,080 --> 00:30:26,400
My phone is dead.

607
00:30:28,810 --> 00:30:29,470
How about this?

608
00:30:29,470 --> 00:30:30,160
You wait for me here.

609
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:30,880
I'll go down to recharge

610
00:30:30,880 --> 00:30:31,440
and make a call.

611
00:30:31,440 --> 00:30:32,400
I'll be right back.

612
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:33,110
Wait for me here.

613
00:30:33,110 --> 00:30:33,830
Okay.

614
00:30:34,050 --> 00:30:35,210
Be careful.

615
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:50,480
Su Qing!

616
00:30:53,280 --> 00:30:54,000
Jiang Lai!

617
00:30:58,920 --> 00:30:59,590
Jiang Lai!

618
00:31:01,400 --> 00:31:02,000
Su Qing!

619
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:03,760
Jiang Lai!

620
00:31:04,340 --> 00:31:05,060
Su Qing!

621
00:31:05,680 --> 00:31:06,610
I'm here!

622
00:31:19,720 --> 00:31:20,480
Zhou Yu.

623
00:31:20,830 --> 00:31:22,050
You saved me again.

624
00:31:28,150 --> 00:31:29,410
What do you like to eat?

625
00:31:30,060 --> 00:31:31,070
You're seriously injured,

626
00:31:31,070 --> 00:31:32,600
yet you still care about what I like to eat?

627
00:31:32,600 --> 00:31:34,760
We don't have much time to be alone.

628
00:31:34,760 --> 00:31:36,490
Of course, I have to cherish it.

629
00:31:36,620 --> 00:31:38,020
So what do you like to eat?

630
00:31:38,520 --> 00:31:40,120
I already have a girlfriend.

631
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:41,880
Do you have any hobbies?

632
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:45,560
I'm still injured.

633
00:31:45,760 --> 00:31:46,760
Slow down.

634
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:48,970
Slow down!

635
00:32:12,810 --> 00:32:13,560
Zhou Yu!

636
00:32:20,230 --> 00:32:21,400
Su Qing, are you okay?

637
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:22,070
I'm fine.

638
00:32:22,210 --> 00:32:22,640
I'm sorry.

639
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:24,100
You got hurt because of me.

640
00:32:24,650 --> 00:32:26,460
This is a blessing in disguise.

641
00:32:26,800 --> 00:32:28,000
Help me open the door.

642
00:32:36,430 --> 00:32:37,030
Zhou Yu...

643
00:32:37,880 --> 00:32:39,040
No matter how familiar you are with this place,

644
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:40,600
you can't climb the mountain at this hour.

645
00:32:40,600 --> 00:32:41,600
Do you know how worried I was

646
00:32:41,600 --> 00:32:43,160
when I only saw Su Qing?

647
00:32:49,470 --> 00:32:50,670
Don't be mad.

648
00:32:50,840 --> 00:32:52,440
I promise I won't do it again.

649
00:32:55,520 --> 00:32:56,530
Don't be mad at me.

650
00:32:58,720 --> 00:32:59,520
Are you okay?

651
00:33:12,560 --> 00:33:13,020
Come in.

652
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:18,730
Chairman.

653
00:33:20,440 --> 00:33:22,510
These are the performance reports

654
00:33:22,540 --> 00:33:24,760
of all our branches for the past two weeks.

655
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:25,820
Please take a look.

656
00:33:28,970 --> 00:33:30,600
How is the resort project?

657
00:33:31,080 --> 00:33:34,000
Mr. Zhou is going through the terms of the contract with Jujiang Capital.

658
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:35,810
Miss Su's resort design plan

659
00:33:35,840 --> 00:33:37,170
has also been approved.

660
00:33:39,280 --> 00:33:42,280
I asked you to investigate Snapdragon Farm last time.

661
00:33:42,600 --> 00:33:44,200
How come you didn't find out

662
00:33:44,220 --> 00:33:46,020
that Jiang Lai is from that farm?

663
00:33:46,600 --> 00:33:48,130
You're not doing a good job.

664
00:33:51,360 --> 00:33:51,960
Chairman.

665
00:33:53,600 --> 00:33:54,200
I'm sorry.

666
00:33:55,000 --> 00:33:56,000
I...

667
00:33:56,360 --> 00:33:57,620
I was careless at work.

668
00:34:09,460 --> 00:34:11,710
The resort project is my main concern.

669
00:34:12,400 --> 00:34:13,860
You know what to do, right?

670
00:34:15,199 --> 00:34:15,960
I know.

671
00:34:16,330 --> 00:34:17,280
I will report everything to you

672
00:34:17,280 --> 00:34:18,719
that happens after that.

673
00:34:19,630 --> 00:34:20,210
Alright.

674
00:34:25,179 --> 00:34:26,500
I bought you a tie.

675
00:34:27,520 --> 00:34:28,380
Try it on later.

676
00:34:32,380 --> 00:34:33,179
Nice tie.

677
00:34:37,260 --> 00:34:37,940
This one...

678
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:39,199
It was on sale.

679
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:40,320
From a friend.

680
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:42,699
Go back to work.

681
00:34:59,450 --> 00:35:02,280
Check Sun Wei's expense record for the month.

682
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:10,160
For the 40th-anniversary celebration

683
00:35:10,160 --> 00:35:11,810
of the company's foundation,

684
00:35:11,210 --> 00:35:14,660
[Announcement of the Administrative Department]

685
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:13,800
the Dream Resort project team

686
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:16,750
will need to present a stage result report

687
00:35:16,950 --> 00:35:19,350
as the key project for the anniversary.

688
00:35:20,540 --> 00:35:22,860
We have just formed a team of designers,

689
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:24,880
and now they want to see our results?

690
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:27,000
I must have done many evil things in my previous life,

691
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:29,860
so I have to work with Mr. Zhou for the rest of my life!

692
00:35:33,140 --> 00:35:33,670
Mr. Zhou.

693
00:35:33,690 --> 00:35:34,690
You caught a cold?

694
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:36,920
Mr. Zhou.

695
00:35:36,920 --> 00:35:38,190
There was a document yesterday...

696
00:35:38,190 --> 00:35:39,120
You're all here!

697
00:35:41,440 --> 00:35:42,700
Special Assistant Li.

698
00:35:43,160 --> 00:35:44,450
You must have seen

699
00:35:44,560 --> 00:35:45,760
the latest group announcement, right?

700
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:46,310
Yes.

701
00:35:47,150 --> 00:35:49,010
The anniversary is approaching.

702
00:35:49,080 --> 00:35:50,940
So, the Chairman has specifically assigned me

703
00:35:50,940 --> 00:35:52,260
to join your project team

704
00:35:52,260 --> 00:35:53,660
to assist with your work.

705
00:35:56,010 --> 00:35:56,610
Mr. Zhou.

706
00:35:57,720 --> 00:35:58,520
I look forward to working with you.
